apter 31</a>, Melisandre I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_39\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 39\">Chapter 39</a>, Jon VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_44\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 44\">Chapter 44</a>, Jon IX.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_49\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 49\">Chapter 49</a>, Jon X.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\">13.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-1\">13.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-2\">13.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_69\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 69\">Chapter 69</a>, Jon XIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-14\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-14\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">georgerrmartin.com: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.georgerrmartin.com/about-george/life-and-times/parris/\">Parris</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_64\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 64\">Chapter 64</a>, Jon VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260408180551\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.111 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.302 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2358/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11342/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 14403/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1827/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 8802/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.45 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  281.111      1 -total\n 88.03%  247.471      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 87.56%  246.143      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.00%   30.916     21 Template:Ref\n 10.80%   30.347     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  6.74%   18.941     21 Template:Ref/core\n  3.18%    8.948      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.65%    4.634      1 Template:References\n  1.32%    3.713      2 Template:Quote\n  0.45%    1.268      2 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cach